item.title: Look Here!
item.dc:creator: @god_of_ikiliki god of ikiliki
item.description:
@god_of_ikiliki wrote:

Go into ur source.
Find the map called “Data”
Open it and somewhere you will see a file called weather.txt
Open it and change the number you see to 3, save it and compile and ur done.

Next time use a normal topic title like need help with dust
The topic title your using people will ingore, lucky Im always viewing it and im not lazy today
